### Terms of Service for HyperGuard

#### 1. Introduction
Welcome to HyperGuard. By using this bot, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following terms and conditions of use. Please read these terms carefully. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must not use our bot.

#### 2. Service Description
HyperGuard is a Discord bot designed to assist with administrative tasks in Roblox games. The bot allows server administrators to ban users from their Roblox games via Discord commands. To enable this functionality, users must provide the bot with the necessary API keys and universe IDs.

